### UseUpRegs {#a32f1c7a8986b0d7bd5a076806bb00b81}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="bool llvm::X86Operand::UseUpRegs = false">

e.g. ARR&#91;eax + ecx&#42;4&#93;, so no extra reg can be used for <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/x86operand/memop">MemOp</a>.
